The main place of my work is the Controlling

00:00:14.860 --> 00:00:17.300
Academy, a joint project of

00:00:17.300 --> 00:00:19.320
the controller of the AG Academy

00:00:19.320 --> 00:00:22.660
of Munich and the German School

00:00:22.660 --> 00:00:23.840
of Business.

